Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,去鲸鱼公园玩警察抓小偷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.87,0:00:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,五年级了还玩警察抓小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,男生真是群小屁孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,二叶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.42,0:00:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,去我房间涂涂看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.64,0:00:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了 走吧
